title: Grateful Dead Live at Madison Square Garden on 1981-03-10
description:
Set 1

Mississippi Half Step-> Franklin's Tower-> Me & My Uncle, Roses> Little Red Rooster, Don't Ease Me In, Lazy Lightning> Supplication, Brown Eyed Women> Looks Like Rain> Deal

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain-> Lost Sailor-> Saint Of Circumstance-> Drums-> The Wheel-> China Doll-> Truckin'-> Sugar Magnolia, E:Satisfaction-> E: Brokedown Palace

reviews.review_text: Wow! This sounds sooooo good! As always, thanks Brother Seamons!
Talkin' to Miss Brown... Such good sound; warm. Great Matrix! It just gets better and better. Love this period of the Dead.
crash! hot show, great recording.  always love hearing the band almost stop, then pick it up again after the crash of the collapsing cymbal stands during 1/2 step;)
